name: Transmogrify and Biscuit
description: An instinctive behavior from birth. "Making biscuits" is when a cat "kneads" a surface. It's generally a sign of a happy and comfortable cat. But it doesn't make you comfortable when your cat Biscuit "makes biscuits". This is because just last night you caught a glimpse of Biscuit's shadow from the other room. It resembled your own.
